    Get observations available

    getObs-methods.Rd

    Get the observations available for a given storm

    getObs(s, ...)

    Arguments

    s

    Storm/StormsList object

    name

    character. Name of the storm to extract in capital letters

    season

    numeric. Cyclonic season of the storm to extract. Used only if several storms in the StormsList object share the same name. Default value is set to NULL

    Value

    data.frame. Observations of the given storm

    Examples

    sts <- Storms(loi = "New Caledonia", names = c("ERICA","NIRAN"))
